name: pyinotify
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.9.6" %}

package:
    name: pyinotify
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: pyinotify-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/p/pyinotify/pyinotify-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 8e580fa1ff3971f94a6f81672b76c406

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [not linux]
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - pyinotify

about:
    home: http://github.com/seb-m/pyinotify
    license: MIT License
    summary: Monitoring filesystems events with inotify on Linux. http://github.com/seb-m/pyinotify/wiki

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - kwilcox
